high_descs: Turn left walk towards the fridge.
Open the shelf, take the grapes from the shelf rack, close the shelf.
Turn around, walk then left and move towards the sink.
Put the grapes into the sink.
Turn around walk towards the sofa and turn left.
Take the grape from the sofa.
Turn left walk towards the sink.
Put the grapes into the sink.
anns.task_desc: To get the grapes from shelf and sofa, put it in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn left and walk head to the fridge.
Pick up the black grape bunch along with leaves next to the food can in the fridge.
Turn back, walk, turn right, walk, and turn left side to the sink.
Put the grape bunch in the sink.
Turn left, walk, and again turn left head to the brown sofa set chair.
Pick up the another black grape bunch along with leaves from the sofa chair.
Turn left, walk, and turn left side to the sink.
Put the another grape bunch along with leaves in front of the first grape bunch in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two black Grape bunches along with leaves in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the fridge.
Pick up the grape from the fridge.
Turn right to reach the sink.
Put the grape in the sink.
Turn left to walk across the room and reach the sofa.
Pick up the grape from the couch.
Turn around to reach the sink.
Put the grape in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two bunches of Grape in the SinkBasin
